  <notes>Spec references: FR-3 (lines 116-122), AC-3b (line 120). Mirror the LookupUserMembershipNodeExecutor pattern strictly (per spec line 261: sibling executor; in-process service invocation pattern). The structured log key is `hallucination_detected` (App Insights query target per docs/guides/AI-MONITORING-DASHBOARD.md). Sentence-level scrubbing is the proposed default behavior; if a configurable scrub-strategy is needed later it can be added in a follow-up task without changing the wire format.</notes>

